/docs/introduction/bayesian-networks/#approximate-inference" title=3D"Direc=
t link to heading">=E2=80=8B</a></h3><ul><li>Wider class of problems</li><l=
i>Deterministic / non deterministic</li><li>No guarantee of correct answer<=
/li></ul><h3 class=3D"anchor anchorWithStickyNavbar_LWe7" id=3D"algorithms"=
